title: Police Force 2
description:
Enter an all new police station, including office rooms and an overview over your statistics and achievements.
15 all new scenarios, plus 60 you already know from "Police Force", such as robbery, securing of evidences, DNA analysis or alcohol controls and interrogations with witnesses.

Use tools, such as weapons, PDAs for identifying suspects and vehicles, handcuffs, radio transceivers and an all new all breath test tool.
Request different vehicles, such as ambulances, wrecking cars as well as prisoner transport vehicles.
Now you can issue cautions for civilians and make use of civil penalties which will increase the realism of each mission
